# Chocolate Date Energy Balls

Based on [Chocolate Date Energy Balls - JoyFoodSunshine](https://joyfoodsunshine.com/paleo-chocolate-brownie-energy-bites) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251230225719/https://joyfoodsunshine.com/paleo-chocolate-brownie-energy-bites/))

